## 11. DuckDB — analytical embedded

[DuckDB](https://duckdb.org) — embedded analytical (OLAP) database. Modern alternative к SQLite для analytics workloads.

### 11.1. Когда DuckDB вместо SQLite

| Workload | SQLite | DuckDB |
|---|---|---|
| OLTP (small transactions) | ✅ | ❌ slower for many small writes |
| OLAP (aggregations / scans) | ❌ slow на large data | ✅ |
| ETL / data analysis | ❌ | ✅ |
| Mixed workload | SQLite default | DuckDB если analytics dominate |

DuckDB — columnar storage, vectorized execution. 10-100x faster than SQLite на analytics queries.

### 11.2. Use cases

- Local data analysis (alternative к pandas / R для tabular workloads)
- Embedded analytics layer в app (например, log aggregation в БД)
- ETL pipelines (read CSV / Parquet, transform, output)
- Notebook-driven analysis (Python / R / etc bindings)

### 11.3. Hybrid pattern

SQLite для OLTP (app state) + DuckDB для analytics (read-only mount of SQLite + analytical queries):

```python
import duckdb

# Attach SQLite as foreign table
duck = duckdb.connect(':memory:')
duck.sql("INSTALL sqlite; LOAD sqlite;")
duck.sql("ATTACH 'app.db' AS app (TYPE SQLITE)")

# Analytical query on SQLite data
duck.sql("""
  SELECT date_trunc('day', occurred_at) AS day, COUNT(*) AS events
  FROM app.events
  WHERE occurred_at > NOW() - INTERVAL 30 DAY
  GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1
""")
```

### 11.4. Parquet integration

DuckDB читает / пишет Parquet files natively — excellent для archive / cold storage / data exchange:

```sql
COPY (SELECT * FROM events WHERE occurred_at < '2025-01-01')
TO 'events-2024.parquet' (FORMAT PARQUET);
```

Compressed columnar storage, queryable directly через DuckDB.

### 11.5. Limitations vs SQLite

- Younger (1.0 release 2024) — less mature ecosystem
- File format менее ubiquitous — нет system tools support
- Concurrent writes — единый writer (как SQLite), но less mature concurrency model
- No FTS — text search через SQL functions

---

## 12. Embedded-specific checklist

В дополнение к `database-design-base.md` § 17:

- [ ] WAL mode enabled (`PRAGMA journal_mode = WAL`)
- [ ] `foreign_keys = ON` enforced
- [ ] STRICT tables для new projects (SQLite 3.37+)
- [ ] Indexes на FK columns (не auto-created)
- [ ] busy_timeout configured (5s+)
- [ ] Encryption strategy — SQLCipher если PII / sensitive (см. § 8) или application-level
- [ ] Backup strategy — sqlite3 backup API или Litestream
- [ ] Restore drill verified (open backup, integrity_check, smoke test)
- [ ] Single-writer constraint understood (если multi-process scenario)
- [ ] FTS5 для text search (если applicable)
- [ ] Migrations через framework (Alembic / Diesel / etc), не raw SQL
- [ ] Если DuckDB для analytics — separate file, не mix OLTP+OLAP в один файл
- [ ] Connection pooling (one-per-thread pattern)
- [ ] Transactions kept short (avoid blocking other writers)
